Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How long...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...do l have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be Suzuna Kuraki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miss Suzuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, l'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,l told you, l don't want you picking me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But Miss, well, this is my job...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,l like being left alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't give up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Yuriko wants to me to escort you to the Kuraki Shrine safely...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...especially now, because your most important ceremony is around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Tomomi-san, do you have any idea what l'm going through at the shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,lf you only knew, maybe you'd understand how l feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The scent of the woods around this time of the year is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,lf l ever have to leave this mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...l'm sure l'll miss it so much that l'll probably have to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,l can go the rest of the way by myself, Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's not like l haven't been doing this for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,l know exactly what to do once l've come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.25,0:04:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,For generations...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...the women of the Kuraki family have been shrinekeepers on Kusaka Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As the highest ranking maidens in service to the Kuraki shrine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...we have been managing the ceremonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My generation is supposed to be a special one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...because l am the shrine maiden for the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...Expecting Moon Ceremony that takes place every few decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuna-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You are quite late today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face looks red.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, l have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take a bath before dinner, Suzuna-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,lio, didn't l tell you to stop calling me Suzuna-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sorry, Suzuna-cha--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,l mean, Suzuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and eat dinner without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,ls something wrong, Suzuna-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,l did it again, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,l was counting on lio to be a hunk when he grew up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...instead, he grew up to be a pretty boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A childhood friend turns into a prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,l guess it doesn't happen in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that man, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who always appears in my dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...and touches me everywhere without my permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, l always feel funny after the ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,l was just checking to see if anybody is here because l heard the noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, l must bring you a change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm fine like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,l just wanted to cool my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do l look funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my point...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,l thought l could understand how you feel a little better if l dress in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,lf you only knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...maybe you could understand how l feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,l am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,lt was a silly idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wild raspberries!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,l love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,l used to look for them on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grandfather brought them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's really sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be careful not to catch a cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To soothe your flushed body after the ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...is also part of my job...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it feel good here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The fuzziness that l always get after the ceremony is going away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,l was dozing off...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Tomomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...last night, the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grandfather thinks the heat must have gone to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't show up at the dinner last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So when l went to look for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You were on the bathroom floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,ls that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Suzuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You are naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,l must have been in such a hurry, l forgot to dress you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Tomomi l've always known...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuriko-sama, was that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was necessary for her to prepare for the Expecting Moon Ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it really a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The touch and everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What am l saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, l am not trying to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not from around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,l wasn't peeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,l was just passing by...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...but l snuck out to take a walk in the woods...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...because l wanted to enjoy the morning sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,l am a TV actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,l am in a show called ''Living in the Mountain'' written by the dramatist...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...who wrote ''From Ohio with Love.''
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever you are, this area is barred to outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You should leave at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,l am not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you forgot this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They are beautiful as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, the gardener must be quite skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like women, flowers require tender care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,l am putting my whole soul to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Gohei-san, l think l warned you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,l suggest not standing behind a woman when you are talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How naughty...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has no manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Suzuna-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you talking about, Suzuna-cha--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,l mean, Suzuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't like him very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,l think he's a bit weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,l sometime can't believe he's Harukawa-san's uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the script for the soap opera that Ruri Yamabe stars in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this Ruri person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:14:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody knows her, she used to be a famous child star...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, l guess l'm not everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...ln that TV commercial for ETO Butter with the Snow Emblem logo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...she became a phenomenon for her cute acting, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,..in that fire scene for the morning TV series ''Glaring eyes'' ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...she impressed everyone by performing her own stunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,ln ''Home Girl'' she played the leading role.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Her line ''l don't want your money, l just want your sympathy'' ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...was the most popular phrase of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the talk of the town, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,lmpressive, you know quite a lot about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Harukawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, well, l'm not a fanatic or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's the sort of information that everybody knows, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,l just knew about her because Suzuna's father is a big fan of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you talk about this kind of thing with him, Suzuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,l haven't even seen him for a half year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even say hi to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother also...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuna-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,l am sorry, l just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,lio...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,l think my mother died a few years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, the camellias look gorgeous today...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Miss Suzuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what were you saying, Suzuna-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,l forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you must get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mizuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,lt doesn't matter if it was a dream or reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That night, l had tasted...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...the forbidden fruit they call ''pleasure.''
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The man in my dream began to appear even when l was awake...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As the secret affair went on, he became accustomed to my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:18:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And just when l was beginning to see his figure clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,l am absolutely not wearing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you wear it then, Sayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't like your temperament.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, it's a custom, you can't run away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell with custom, There's no way l'm going to get married to a guy l haven't met!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Suzuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be so difficult, Suzuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuna, your marriage was arranged by your grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...not only that, it's your father's last wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't know if he really passed away or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He has been missing from this mansion for a year without even a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He is no longer qualified to lead the Kuraki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you must prepare yourself for the bridal bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your husband is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you help Suzuna freshen up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't need any help with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...Tomomi is really good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kuraki's thousand years of history hinges on your marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,l-l think they suit you..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use whichever you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:19:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Except this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't need any.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,l-lt seems your husband is exhausted from traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So please be easy on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm the one he needs to be easy on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got some nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already made himself at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He is kinda okay-looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's just like the one in my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You horny bastard, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at first l thought she might be an angel, but now l know l was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.37,0:22:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time for Suzuna, so you should be the one to lead her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.68,0:22:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't care who you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...but l want you to explain what's going on here so l can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That Camellia tree is very important to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.13,0:22:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That pond exists only because of the tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,l am going to kick him out, definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.69,0:23:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,l will talk to my grandmother myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.03,0:23:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come in without knocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.58,0:23:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.22,0:23:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:23:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.70,0:24:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.93,0:24:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.38,0:24:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.17,0:28:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,lt is the fate of all flowers to bloom and fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.30,0:28:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Sayaka Kurihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.37,0:28:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm a maid at the Kuraki Mansion, l take care of Miss Suzuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.91,0:28:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...and before that, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.21,0:28:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am l?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.69,0:28:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Moonlight Lady, second night: Sunflower.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.26,0:28:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,On sale in spring of 2002.
